You can go see Vasu first.

231
00:28:13,368 --> 00:28:14,909
Let the kid go ahead.
-Yes, sir.

232
00:28:23,410 --> 00:28:25,451
Your son is here to see you.

233
00:28:25,576 --> 00:28:26,702
I'll send him in.

234
00:28:26,826 --> 00:28:28,159
In here?

235
00:28:28,285 --> 00:28:29,993
We usually meet in the visiting area.

236
00:28:30,118 --> 00:28:33,118
If you want to see him here, do it.
If not, I'll send him away.

237
00:28:33,243 --> 00:28:35,326
He'd be anticipating this.
I'll see him here.

238
00:28:35,451 --> 00:28:37,493
Can you take off these cuffs, please?

239
00:28:37,618 --> 00:28:39,034
Let him not see me with these.

240
00:28:39,702 --> 00:28:42,867
When you come in here,
forget about your dignity!

241
00:28:42,993 --> 00:28:46,326
This is how you will see him.
If you don't want to, I'll send him away!

242
00:28:54,201 --> 00:28:55,826
How did you take them off?

243
00:28:55,951 --> 00:28:57,034
Hey!
Release me!

244
00:28:58,034 --> 00:29:00,159
Let the Chief see
what kind of person he is.

245
00:29:00,285 --> 00:29:03,118
Someone might see this!
I'll be ruined on my first day here!

246
00:29:03,243 --> 00:29:04,951
I beg of you!
Let me loose!

247
00:29:05,076 --> 00:29:08,368
